items.headline: Welcome to Survival of the Fittest Wikia
items.desc: Survival of the Fittest Wikia is a Battle Royale based roleplaying site. The premise of the game is simple: you are a student who, along with the rest of your class, has been thrown onto an island, fitted with an explosive collar, issued a weapon, and given the ultimate ultimatum: kill or be killed. Survival of the Fittest, more commonly known as "SOTF", differs from its inspiration in that unlike most BR-oriented roleplays, SOTF has its own unique storyline, unique characters, and a whole plethora of unexpected happenings. Interested yet? You should be. Battle Royale never got this extreme.

items.headline: Enter The Deadworld Survival Wiki
items.desc: This wiki is an role-playing wiki. After a virus known as CANV-11 (which you can read about on the wiki) takes over the world, most humans and animals become infected. You create a survival group, create a leader who you will role-play as, and then enter the "Deadworld", the name given to this post-apocalyptic Earth. Although you can only start with a maximum of fifteen characters and have a base in one of forty territories in either New York, Chicago, and Los Angeles, over time, you will spread to more foreign lands and dominate the world as a ruthless dictator or a peaceful leader. Your choice...

items.name: Survivor ORG Wiki
items.title: Survivor ORG Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to Survivor ORG Wiki
items.desc: Survivor (also known as Expedition Robinson in some regions) is a reality game show produced in many countries throughout the world. In the show, contestants are isolated in the wilderness and compete for cash and other prizes. The show uses a system of progressive elimination, allowing the contestants to vote off other tribe members until only one final contestant remains and wins the title of "Sole Survivor." The format for Survivor was created in 1992 by the British television producer Charlie Parsons for a United Kingdom TV production company called Planet 24, but the Swedish version, shown in 1997, was the first Survivor series to actually make it to television.

items.title: KidA's Survivor Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Kida's Survivor Wikia!
items.desc: KidA, or Ryan, is the host of KidA's Survivor Series, which began on January 24th. Ryan joined Tengaged on December 12, 2011, and has created several twists for his game, such as, the Ghost Town twist, the Viper Idol twist, and the Island Vault twist. If you have a question for Ryan, feel free to leave him one on his ask.fm!

items.name: Survivor Z Wiki
items.title: Survivor Z Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Survivor Z Wiki!
items.desc:
Survivor Z is a location-based iPhone game that allows users to 'search' foursquare locations to find food, water and supplies to survive the game's apocalyptic zombie scenario.  The game has a very reasonable price tag and is a lot of fun to play if you tend to move around.  
This Wiki is designed to help players get through encounters they are stuck on.  If you know of a location that has a specific encounter that isn't listed on the site, feel free to add it or let the admin know so they can get to work on a page for the location.

items.name: DrPanda Gaming Wiki
items.title: DrPanda Gaming Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the DrPanda Survivor ORG Wiki!
items.desc:
This site is the Survivor ORG (Online Reality Game) created by Survivorpanda and TheDrPeps79 to simulate the Survivor experience, except it's online. Anyone who wants to play in a season can simply ask and they will be cast in the upcoming game.

This wiki has all the info on the settings, contestants, and drama of the full simulated Survivor experience.

items.name: SurvivalCraft Wiki
items.title: SurvivalCraft Wiki
items.headline: Survive the SurvivalCraft Wiki!
items.desc: SurvivalCraft is about you being marooned on an island by a ship you were traveling in, which as they say in-game, will never come back for you. With only your hands and the scraps of clothing on your back to depend on you'll have to make the best of your situation. You'll have to survive for as long as you can, which means trying to take advantage of your permanent stay on the never ending island. Discover rare animals, gather resources, hunt for food, fight off the carnivores that come after you at night and more!
